# Footer

## Layout
Three column grid on desktop, single column stacked on mobile.
Bottom bar below a divider line.

## Column 1 — Brand
- SD logo (same pattern as Navbar — dark/light switching)
- Logo size: 48x48px
- Short tagline below logo:
  "Building enterprise platforms that scale."
- Tagline: Inter 14px, var(--text-muted)

## Column 2 — Quick Links
- Heading: "Quick Links" — Space Grotesk 13px bold uppercase tracking-widest
- Links: INTRO, ABOUT, PROJECTS, SKILLS, JOURNEY, CONTACT
- Each scrolls to its section id on click
- Same scrollToSection pattern as Navbar
- Style: Inter 14px, var(--text-secondary), hover var(--text-primary)
- Mark each with // TODO: wire up when section is built

## Column 3 — Contact
- Heading: "Contact" — same heading style as Quick Links
- Items:
  - Email icon + "samdsiva1994@gmail.com" — mailto link
  - LinkedIn icon + "LinkedIn" — placeholder href="#"
  - GitHub icon + "GitHub" — placeholder href="#"
  - MessageSquare icon + "Leave a Message" — placeholder, scrolls to #contact
- Icons from lucide-react: Mail, Linkedin, Github, MessageSquare
- Style: Inter 14px, var(--text-secondary), hover var(--text-primary)
- flex items-center gap-2 per item

## Divider
- 1px border-t border-[var(--border)] above bottom bar

## Bottom Bar
- Left: "© 2026 Sam Dhanalakota. All rights reserved."
  Inter 13px var(--text-muted)
- Right: "Back to top ↑" button
  Scrolls to #intro on click
  Inter 13px var(--text-muted) hover var(--text-primary)
- justify-between items-center

## Outer Container
- bg-[var(--bg-secondary)]
- border-t border-[var(--border)]
- px-6 md:px-10 py-16

## Rules
- "use client" required (scrollToSection, mounted state)
- Logo switches dark/light same as Navbar using mounted + theme
- No hardcoded colors
- All placeholders marked with comments